      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING ADMIRAL (3) is yet to miss the placings in an excellent record this track and trip which boasts three wins and two placings. In the money last time at this track (18.10) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 0.8 lengths second. Looks suited and should go close. FEAR TO EXCEL (7) was always well back but did hit the line strongly late to finish 4th and beaten only 2.5 lengths (18.24) at this track. Returns to a course where she has performed well. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to her credit. Likely to play a prominent role. I'M BORED (1) was in the minors when resuming at this track where she finished third (18.45) in a Grade 4/5. Will strip fitter for the run. Expected to be in this for a long way. RAINY DREAM (8) was well supported last time but could only manage second (18.42), beaten a nose. Overdue and is among the main hopes.",
